# ==========================================
# Comments & Notes
# ==========================================
# This .gitignore is designed for the M³GIM project
#
# What we DO track:
# - All Python scripts (preprocessing/, scripts/)
# - All documentation (docs/, *.md)
# - Processed JSON data (data/*.json)
# - HTML catalog (archive_catalog.html)
# - Templates (templates/)
# - Tests (tests/)
# - GitHub Actions workflows (.github/workflows/)
# - Controlled vocabularies (data/vocabularies/*.json)
#
# What we DON'T track:
# - Large source files (*.xlsx, *.pdf)
# - Generated files (__pycache__, *.pyc)
# - Credentials (.env, secrets.json)
# - IDE settings (.vscode/, .idea/)
# - OS files (.DS_Store, Thumbs.db)
# - Virtual environments (venv/)
#
# For sensitive data:
# - Source Excel file should remain on Google Sheets
# - PDF scans hosted externally (university server)
# - Credentials stored in GitHub Secrets
#
# See STRUCTURE.md for full folder organization
